<L>__{exterior lucky star motel night}
<A>__{bernie's 1958 buick electra pulls into the parking lot of a flea bag motel. next door to the motel, we see a convenience store with the name, the ez mark in pink glowing neon. it's actually supposed to read: the ez market, but the last two letters of "market" have burned out.}
<L>__{interior lucky star motel courtyard night}
<A>__{one of those center pool style motels. a hard luck oasis, if ever there was one. as bernie limps toward his room, his neighbor, a low rent hooker, approaches from the opposite end of the courtyard with a huge ass john in tow. they converge at their doors at the same time. there's a weariness about the hooker that's endemic to this town. she winks at bernie. he nods at her. then casts a furtive glance over at the john. the man flips him off. the hooker mouths, "sorry." bernie hastily enters his apartment.}
